    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Dei et salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos, <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis" ref="#people/2000"
                            >Grimoaldus</persName>, Dei previdencia, Beneventane provincie <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, per rogum <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Other_palatine_officer"><name ref="Audoaldus"
                                >Aodoaldi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">referendarii</rs> nostri, in <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Fines #Landed_possessions #Curtes #Mountains"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1900">Sancti Vincencii martyris</orgName>, qui
                        situs est in finibus Samnie, iuxta <placeName key="#Rivers"
                            ref="#places/609">Vulturno</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Rivers">flumine</rs>, ubi venerabilis vir <persName key="#Abbots"
                            ref="#people/2001">Iosue</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> custos esse videtur, <rs key="#Curtes">curtem
                            nostram</rs>, quam habemus in <rs key="#Fines">finibus</rs> territorio
                            <geogName
                            key="#Fines #Landed_possessions #Curtes #Mountains #Rivers #Roads"
                            ref="#estates/1901">Benafrano</geogName>, cum inclitis <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et montibus uno se tenente, et
                        vocatur terra ipsa <geogName
                            key="#Rivers #Mountains #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Roads"
                            ref="#estates/1900">Cicerana</geogName>, per hos fines: prima parte
                        riagine que nominatur <placeName key="#Rivers">Ravennola</placeName>, unde
                        per tempus aqua decurrit; secunda parte iam dicto fluvio <placeName
                            key="#Rivers" ref="#places/609">Vulturno</placeName>; tercia parte <rs
                            key="#Roads">via</rs> et silice, et quomodo ascendit riagine usque in
                        cilium montis de ipsa curte pertinentes; quarta vero parte terras et <rs
                            key="#Mountains">montes puplici</rs>. Ideo in iam dicto monasterio
                        concessimus in integrum iam dictas terras et montes per iam dictos fines
                        possidendum, in ea videlicet racione, ut a modo et deinceps per hoc nostrum
                        roboratum preceptum cuncta, ut superius leguntur, tibi iam dicto Iosue
                        venerabili abbati atque successoribus et rectoribus vestri monasterii
                        securiter habere et possidere valeatis, ita ut a nullis ex nostris
                        iudicibus, idest comitibus seu castaldeis, vel a quibuscumque hominibus non
                        habeatis de predictas terras et montes aliquam requisicionem, sed perpetuis
                        temporibus possideatis. Quod vero preceptum, ex iussione tue potestatis,
                        scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/110" key="#Cities #Palatium">Benevento</placeName>,
                        in <rs key="#Palatium">sacro palacio</rs> mense aprilis, tercia indiccione,
                        feliciter.</ab>
